  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/9fef91d78f830d724aef83dca2d75e02.poster.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/9fef91d78f830d724aef83dca2d75e02.webm?t=1767633081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this romantic, slice-of visual novel, you take the role of a new student admitted to Weather Vane, a secret school for magic hidden beneath the foggy city of London. As you attend the school and grow closer to your classmates, you'll learn more about their individual stories and their personal struggles with magic. Along the way, you'll find friendships, love, and perhaps a bright future for all.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/9505447cdf3e4db9f861a19ce542d0b6.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/a2a18b3cdb721b587e2642cca5b337da.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weather Van is magical school built on three floating islands that exist in a pocket dimension beneath 1950s London. Enjoy trips to the city on the surface and wondrous sights only possible through magic.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/5542572a498ea0d8757b51f6faa8856e.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices will lead to many different places including the different stories of the five main heroines, three side routes, one hidden route, and three bonus stories.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/2d0abde7a9c2ae459c8ae0b672b6ea83.poster.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/2d0abde7a9c2ae459c8ae0b672b6ea83.webm?t=1767633081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day you'll have several choices on where to go and what to do, allowing you to spend time with the different characters and cultivate your bonds with them. These choices, along with your dialogue choices, will determine how your story progresses.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/bd32b642460f5d09fe61a89cdfa8882b.poster.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/bd32b642460f5d09fe61a89cdfa8882b.webm?t=1767633081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/c9364aa352d9aa2b31e10d448cf0b772.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/740052784ef390e6dc3eb50c41188b02.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/c9f49ba950d19b76417156156bb838df.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/3e61783cc04176dd55c82b7f42f6ca96.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/69549fccebf38a0af4d1606f981f7c08.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/58e1478b1840c3f238aa2f5149152db0.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Much like the music term the title is derived from, the story will build and deepen with every playthrough. Each route will reveal new information about the characters and the setting, but there will be subtle differences that grow as well until the tale being woven reaches its true finale.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/9fef91d78f830d724aef83dca2d75e02.poster.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/9fef91d78f830d724aef83dca2d75e02.webm?t=1767633081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this romantic, slice-of visual novel, you take the role of a new student admitted to Weather Vane, a secret school for magic hidden beneath the foggy city of London. As you attend the school and grow closer to your classmates, you'll learn more about their individual stories and their personal struggles with magic. Along the way, you'll find friendships, love, and perhaps a bright future for all.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/9505447cdf3e4db9f861a19ce542d0b6.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/a2a18b3cdb721b587e2642cca5b337da.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weather Van is magical school built on three floating islands that exist in a pocket dimension beneath 1950s London. Enjoy trips to the city on the surface and wondrous sights only possible through magic.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/5542572a498ea0d8757b51f6faa8856e.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices will lead to many different places including the different stories of the five main heroines, three side routes, one hidden route, and three bonus stories.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/2d0abde7a9c2ae459c8ae0b672b6ea83.poster.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/2d0abde7a9c2ae459c8ae0b672b6ea83.webm?t=1767633081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day you'll have several choices on where to go and what to do, allowing you to spend time with the different characters and cultivate your bonds with them. These choices, along with your dialogue choices, will determine how your story progresses.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/bd32b642460f5d09fe61a89cdfa8882b.poster.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/bd32b642460f5d09fe61a89cdfa8882b.webm?t=1767633081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/c9364aa352d9aa2b31e10d448cf0b772.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/542290/extras/740052784ef390e6dc3eb50c41188b02.avif?t=1767633081\" width=780 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"